OL,3,CDoctors failed to tell a father of
OL,4,Cseven he was terminally ill
OL,6,FDoctors failed to tell a father-of-
OL,7,Fseven he was terminally ill and
OL,8,Finstead said he would be OK, an
OL,9,Finvestigation has found.
OL,11,FWilliam Chapman, known as Syd, only
OL,12,Fdiscovered he had deadly pulmonary
OL,13,Ffibrosis when his GP ` who thought he
OL,14,Falready knew his prognosis ` mentioned
OL,15,Fit during a phone call.
OL,17,FMr Chapman died eight months later.
