OL,3,CDoctors failed to tell a father of
OL,4,Cseven he was terminally ill
OL,6,FNow, an investigation by the
OL,7,FParliamentary and Health Service
OL,8,FOmbudsman (PHSO) has found that
OL,9,Fdoctors at the Countess of Chester
OL,10,FHospital showed a "worrying lack of
OL,11,Faccountability" and failed to keep
OL,12,Fproper records, engage fully with Mr
OL,13,FChapman's family or learn from
OL,14,Fmistakes.
OL,16,FMr Chapman, 58, from Upton, Cheshire,
OL,17,Fwas a grandfather-of-16 and died in
OL,18,F2022.
OL,26,@rD@SOUsD@OO]
