OL,3,CDoctors failed to tell a father of
OL,4,Cseven he was terminally ill
OL,6,FMr Chapman's daughter Chantelle, 32,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We feel completely let down by
OL,8,Fthe Trust.
OL,10,F"My dad thought he was going to get
OL,11,Fbetter, because that's what they led
OL,12,Fhim to believe. Because of that he
OL,13,Fcarried on working, even though it was
OL,14,Fa struggle for him.
OL,16,F"If he had known the truth, he would
OL,17,Fhave given up work and made the most
OL,18,Fof the time he had left with his
OL,19,Ffamily.
OL,26,@oD@GOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
