OL,3,CDoctors failed to tell a father of
OL,4,Cseven he was terminally ill
OL,6,FThe PHSO found no failings in clinical
OL,7,Fcare.
OL,9,FRebecca Hilsenrath KC, chief executive
OL,10,Fofficer at PHSO, said: "This
OL,11,Fdisturbing case highlights the
OL,12,Fimportance of effective communication
OL,13,Fand the consequences of getting it
OL,14,Fwrong.
OL,16,F"When you hear this kind of diagnosis
OL,17,Fin this kind in this way, you lose a
OL,18,Fsense of dignity and the opportunity
OL,19,Fto make your own decisions about how
OL,20,Fto live your life.
OL,26,@rD@XOUxD@AOU
