OL,3,CDoctors failed to tell a father of
OL,4,Cseven he was terminally ill
OL,6,F"The family's trauma was compounded by
OL,7,Ftheir treatment during the hospital's
OL,8,Finternal complaints handling."
OL,10,FShe said a previous PHSO report
OL,11,Fhighlighted "too little accountability
OL,12,Fand too much defensiveness in the
OL,13,FNHS", adding there needs to be a
OL,14,F"cultural shift starting from the top
OL,15,Fdown to improve patient safety and
OL,16,Favoid further harm".
