OL,3,CDoctors failed to tell a father of
OL,4,Cseven he was terminally ill
OL,6,F"We routinely see Trusts fail to
OL,7,Faccept errors or acknowledge the
OL,8,Fimpact, which causes complainants more
OL,9,Fdistress at what is already a
OL,10,Fdifficult time."
OL,12,FThe trust has complied with a
OL,13,Frecommendation to apologise, make
OL,14,Fservice improvements, improve its
OL,15,Frecord keeping, and pay Mr Chapman's
OL,16,Fwife #1,200.
